name: Bullion Confection Side Table Circular S
description: The Bullion Side Table Medium is inspired by stacked gold bars. Available in a small size to create a nesting set. Currently made to order 8-10 weeks. Design SKU reference KST02CS. Handmade; Antique Natural Shagreen surface, bronze-patina brass legs; Wipe clean with soft dry cloth; Made in Philippines. Although inspired by her parents, Kifu's collection has a distinct identity characterized by handmade techniques and materials like shagreen, shells, and semi-precious stones, reflecting a mix of traditional craftsmanship and youthful design elements.
